  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency expect-jsx to v4",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx\">expect-jsx</a> from <code>v2.6.0</code> to <code>v4.0.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>algolia/expect-jsx</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"400\">4.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/17e40bed3533e6620f43fe3ddf3abb187c9f0fb3\"><code>17e40be</code></a> 4.0.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"310\">3.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/7d226ec918b3d5e114a578e53fc46ddd755a7d94\"><code>7d226ec</code></a> Merge pull request #&#8203;27 from kjs3/bump-react-element-to-jsx-string-version</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/edf5fa5681ea1baf143b585f6d3d3b9adb9e593f\"><code>edf5fa5</code></a> yarn.lock update</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/efbfd062a685fbf48a69d6eb73c02cc94bf38e30\"><code>efbfd06</code></a> Putting React devDep back.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/97f7caf94b2a34abea98880feb259f6a1c28b916\"><code>97f7caf</code></a> Bumping react-element-to-jsx-string way up to v12.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/e698ff33273aebe5c37666b6091025a9fb3f5a37\"><code>e698ff3</code></a> Resolving yarn module collision warning.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"300\">3.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/b5960cf9cf67bc65558e5ce01e8e38afbde95866\"><code>b5960cf</code></a> 3.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/f6723fe4ffce0330989fc6c67e14cb085888663e\"><code>f6723fe</code></a> chore(release): chmod +x</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/4fc435f306bc1bda18001d3ed8965ebae3958b15\"><code>4fc435f</code></a> docs(README): add not about releasing</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/5149e6c63138422d3cbb86a5b697386eba20d083\"><code>5149e6c</code></a> docs(README): add note about ES2015</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/a01467252fa12fa9ad79e58cab6aea4e861a3a8f\"><code>a014672</code></a> chore(lib): upgrade to react-element-to-jsx-string latest</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/algolia/expect-jsx/commit/44ee04df570a47b3b6f3f6c376b99e5dcfbcd066\"><code>44ee04d</code></a> chore(lib): cleanup lib, upgrade deps</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
